title: TrainSimple - Business Catalyst Fundamentals
description: Business Catalyst (BC) is an all-in-one business website and online marketing solution, built for web designers. You can build everything from amazing websites to powerful online stores, beautiful brochure-ware sites, and lead generation mini-sites all without back-end coding. Join BC expert Scott Reynolds of Thrise.com in this fundamentals course so you can get started building online businesses.
